item.title: CVE-2023-46699|2024-09-12T12:36:17.923Z -- weseek%2C%20inc. -- growi
item.description: Cross-site request forgery (CSRF) vulnerability exists in the User settings (/me) page of GROWI versions prior to v6.0.0. If a user views a malicious page while logging in, settings may be changed without the user's intention.
